orithms\", \"NoSuchAlgorithm:SUN\");\ntry { System.out.println(SecureRandom.getInstanceStrong()); } catch (Exception e) { e.printStackTrace(); }\nEOF", "timeout": 20}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 802, "output": 1808, "cacheRead": 39424, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 42034, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780870210825, "responseId": "resp_0eb6df6e03b175a4016a25ec44657081969f8c9cf6e6cb6e63"}}
