e=not-a-url`\n    - `securerandom.strongAlgorithms=NoSuchAlgorithm:SUN`\n  - Added a setup assertion that `SecureRandom.getInstanceStrong()` now throws `NoSuchAlgorithmException`, proving the test environment will drive Bouncy Castle into `DRBG.findSource(...)`.\n\n- Added service registration:\n  - `tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk18on/1.77/src/test/resources/META-INF/services/org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.Extension`\n\n- Updated `build.gradle`\n  - Enabled JUnit extension autodetection for JVM tests.\n  - Enabled the same property for `nativeTest`.\n  - Kept the required `--add-opens=java.base/sun.security.provider=ALL-UNNAMED` for reflective access to the JDK fallback entropy provider classes.\n\nFiles changed:\n\n- `tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk18on/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk18on/DRBGTest.java`\n- `tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk18on/1.77/src/test/resources/META-INF/services/org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.Extension`\n- `tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk18on/1.77/build.gradle`\n\nI did not run the Gradle test command.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0eb6df6e03b175a4016a25ed499ab481969004ee30b3c55318\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 809, "output": 853, "cacheRead": 51200, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 52862, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780870458739, "responseId": "resp_0eb6df6e03b175a4016a25ed3be80c8196b21ef97d536d4a41"}}
